== Itihas ==
[[फायल:Mausoléo_São_Francisco_Xavier.jpg|thumb|St. Francis Xavierscheo reliko<br /><ref>{{cite web|author=|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-11-12/goa/30390942_1_iffi-novena-baretto|title=Church slams govt over Iffi dates, threat to Old Goa - Times Of India|publisher=Articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com|date=2011-11-12|accessdate=2013-12-04}}</ref>]]
[[फायल:Goa_-_St._Francis_Xavier's_Church.JPG|thumb|Igorjecho sozoilolo darvontto.]]
Igorjecho  bandavollicho  vavr 1594 vorsa suru zalo. Mai 1605 vorsa Igorjechem somorponn  korpant ailem jem Arsebisp Dom Padri. Aleixo de Menezes hannem kelem. Hi jagotik iadostik Kristi itihasant ek mhotvachi ghoddnuk zavn asa,.Tantunt [[Sam Fransisku Xaviera Gaoin|St. Francis Xavier]] hachi kudd asa, zo ek  [[Loyolacho St. Inas]] hacho lagxilo ixtt aslo zannem [[Society of Jesus]] ([[Jezuit]]) sthapli. Francis Xavier jen’na to [[Chin]] bhuimkhonddak viaj martalo,to Sancian zunvear somplo (Dezembr 3, 1552).
Francis Xavier hachi kudd poilim Purtugez Malacca vhorpant aili ani don vorsam uprant Goeant bottintlean patthovpant aili, Ti nikipiloli tea vellar asli toxich taji asli oxem sangpant ieta.<ref name="BDS">{{cite web|url=http://www.lakehouse.lk/budusarana/2006/01/29/Budu13.pdf|title=Ven. Thotagamuwe Sri Rahula Thera Scholar monk par excellence|publisher=Lake House|date=29 January 2006|accessdate=1 October 2013|author=Himbutana, Gopitha Peiris}}</ref> Santacheo vosti pollovnk ozun bhonvddekaranchi (zantunt Kristi toxench on-Kristi aspavtat) sonvsar bhorcho chodd korun dor dha vorsamni (nimannem  2014 vorsa korpant ailam) bhovxik dakhovnnent gordi zata. Santak ojapanchem pekovnnechem boll asa oxem somzotat.
Bharotant ani Goeant hi sogllea von pornni Igorz zavn asa. Ladi paxannachi asa zantunt moladik fator korantpant aileat. Vorixtt bhangracho lep kaddlolea altaram xivai, Igorjechem bhitorlem sozovop  sadem zavn asa. Mukhel altaracher ek vhodd [[Loyolacho St. Inas]], zo [[Society of Jesus]] ([[Jezuit]]) sthapnar aslo ani  Francis Xavieracho ek sangati aslo,tachi murti asa zachea hea utram udexim to aplem jivit bodlunk pavlo. "Sonvsar jikhlear kiteak upkarta punn aplo otmo ibaddlear?" Ignatius hannem Fransisak oso vichar kelo?" 


[[फायल:Main_altar_at_the_Basilica_of_Bom_Jesus.jpg|thumb|Baroque xoilichea mukhel  altarak bhangaracho  lep asa  ani thoim  Solomonic khambeam modem Loyolachea St, Inas-achi murti asa, Jezuchim poilim okxoram  IHS  ani Povitr Otmo boroilolem melltta]]
Bhangracho lep kaddlolea  Loyolachea Inas-ache murticho chokmok voir tharailea Jezuchea nanvam vordhan  (IHS) bhangracho lep kaddlolea Jezuitanchea nixannicher asa, zo chokmokit kirnnamni revddailolo asa. Nixannicher, [[Povitr Atmo]] -- Bap, Put ani Povitr Atmo --  xevttachem kavio ani dhormixtt Kristanvancho kendrbindu asa. Altarachem mez jem Povitr Misant vaporpant ieta takai bhangracho lep asa ani tacher Kristachim chitram ani Nimannea Jevnnache xisanche fottu distat zacher him utram asat "Hi Mhoji Kudd",  jim Somorponnachim Utram zavn asat.

Igorjent St,Fransis Xavier-achea jivitachea dekhaveanchim chitram distat. Voir aslolem  thoddeavelem iadostik jem eka chandiechea  kaxanvant asa. St. Francis Xavier (1696), hachi kudd aslolo kaxanv Medicis, Cosimo III, hea Grand Duke of Tuscany hachi ek bhett zavn asa.

Thoddeavelem iadostik 17vea xekddeantlea Florentine xilpkar  Giovanni Battista Foggini hannim ankhnni kelea. Taka tem purnn korpak dha vorsam laglim. Santachi kudd aslolo kaxanv chandiecho  zavn asa. Povitr santacheo reliko dor dha vorsant dakhovnnenk dovorpat ietat jen’na tachea mornnacho dis somorpant ieta. Tachea sevadhormachi porob 3 Dezembrak korpant ieta.

Kaxanvachea voir, voilea thorar, Bom Jesus Bazilikechi Kolechi Agaxi asa zantunt Goenchea ovastovik chitrkar [[Dom Martin]] hachim chitram  asat.

Borovpi ani sangati Jezuit Anthony De Mello hovui  Goencho aslo zoi aplea borovpant bazilikecho ul’lekh korta. Kuddichem dorxon dor dha vorsant korpant ieta.

Bom Jezuchi Bazilika  408 vorsa von odik pornni asa ani dor disa bhovsak pollovpak ugti asa, St. Francis Xavier hachi kudd eka borea sozoilolea kaxavant asa zo sokoilea fottvant pollovpant ieta. Povitr ‘kuddicheo’ dakhovnneo  dor dha vorsant korpant ietat. Tea kallache kolechea vavrachi somzut mellche khatir, Thodde Igorjeche bhitorle fottu hanga zoddleat Hea kolechea vavrak, “murals”; mhonnpant ietat. 

